(================================================================================) Tj T*
(CENTRAL RESERVE POLICE FORCE \(CRPF\)) Tj T*
(DIRECTORATE GENERAL   ENGINEERING WING) Tj T*
(CGO Complex, Lodhi Road, New Delhi   110003) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(NOTICE INVITING TENDER \(NIT\)) Tj T*
(Tender Reference No.: CRPF/EW/2025-26/BOP-RAJ/0042) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Subject: CONSTRUCTION OF 06 \(SIX\) BORDER OUTPOST BUILDINGS IN RAJASTHAN SECTOR) Tj T*
(         \(BARMER AND JAISALMER DISTRICTS\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(GeM Bid Number: GEM/2025/B/5234871) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Published on: Central Public Procurement Portal \(CPPP\) & GeM) Tj T*
(Date of Publication: 15th April 2025) Tj T*
(Last Date for Submission of Bids: 20th May 2025 \(1400 hrs IST\)) Tj T*
(Date of Opening of Technical Bids: 21st May 2025 \(1100 hrs IST\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Estimated Cost: Rs. 18,50,00,000/- \(Rupees Eighteen Crore Fifty Lakh Only\)) Tj T*
(Earnest Money Deposit \(EMD\): Rs. 37,00,000/- \(Rupees Thirty-Seven Lakh Only\)) Tj T*
(Performance Security: 3% of contract value as ePBG) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 1: INTRODUCTION AND SCOPE OF WORK) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.1  The Director General, CRPF, invites sealed tenders \(Two-Bid System   ) Tj T*
(     Technical Bid and Financial Bid\) from eligible contractors for the ) Tj T*
(     construction of 06 \(six\) Border Outpost \(BOP\) buildings in Rajasthan ) Tj T*
(     Sector, as per the specifications and terms laid down in this document.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.2  The work involves:) Tj T*
(     \(a\) Construction of 06 BOP buildings \(each approx. 450 sqm built-up area\)) Tj T*
(     \(b\) Internal electrification and plumbing) Tj T*
(     \(c\) Solar power installation \(5 KW per BOP\)) Tj T*
(     \(d\) Water harvesting structure at each location) Tj T*
(     \(e\) Perimeter fencing \(chain-link, 8 ft height\)) Tj T*
(     \(f\) Approach road construction \(WBM + BT surface, 200m per BOP\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.3  Period of Completion: 12 months from the date of issue of Work Order.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.4  Defect Liability Period: 24 months from the date of completion.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 2: ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Bidders must satisfy ALL of the following eligibility criteria. Failure to ) Tj T*
(meet any mandatory criterion will result in rejection of the bid.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.1  FINANCIAL CRITERIA) Tj T*
(                        ) Tj T*
(2.1.1  Annual Turnover: The bidder must have an average annual turnover of ) Tj T*
(       not less than Rs. 5 Crore \(Rupees Five Crore\) during the last three ) Tj T*
(       financial years \(FY 2022-23, FY 2023-24, FY 2024-25\), as certified ) Tj T*
(       by a Chartered Accountant.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.1.2  Net Worth: The bidder must have a positive net worth as on 31st March ) Tj T*
(       2025, certified by a Chartered Accountant.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.1.3  Solvency Certificate: The bidder must submit a Solvency Certificate ) Tj T*
(       from a Scheduled Bank for an amount not less than Rs. 3 Crore.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.2  EXPERIENCE CRITERIA) Tj T*
(                         ) Tj T*
(2.2.1  Similar Work Experience: The bidder must have successfully completed ) Tj T*
(       at least TWO \(2\) similar works \(construction of government/defense ) Tj T*
(       buildings\) of value not less than Rs. 7 Crore each, OR ONE \(1\) similar ) Tj T*
(       work of value not less than Rs. 12 Crore, during the last SEVEN \(7\) ) Tj T*
(       years ending 31st March 2025.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.2.2  Government Contract Experience: The bidder must have experience of ) Tj T*
(       executing at least one contract with a Central/State Government ) Tj T*
(       department or Public Sector Undertaking \(PSU\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.3  TECHNICAL CRITERIA) Tj T*
(                        ) Tj T*
(2.3.1  Registration: The bidder must be registered as a contractor with ) Tj T*
(       CPWD / MES / State PWD / Railways in Class-I or equivalent category.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.3.2  ISO Certification: The bidder should possess a valid ISO 9001:2015 ) Tj T*
(       Quality Management System certification.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.3.3  Labour License: The bidder must hold a valid Contract Labour License ) Tj T*
(       under the Contract Labour \(Regulation and Abolition\) Act, 1970.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.4  COMPLIANCE CRITERIA) Tj T*
(                         ) Tj T*
(2.4.1  GST Registration: The bidder must have a valid GST Registration ) Tj T*
(       \(GSTIN\) and must be compliant with GST return filing.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.4.2  PAN Card: The bidder must submit a copy of the PAN Card.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.4.3  No Blacklisting: The bidder must submit a self-declaration that the ) Tj T*
(       firm has not been blacklisted or debarred by any Central/State ) Tj T*
(       Government department or PSU as on the date of bid submission.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.4.4  EMD Submission: The bidder must submit EMD of Rs. 37,00,000/- in the ) Tj T*
(       form of BG/FDR/DD in favour of "Pay & Accounts Officer, CRPF".) Tj T*
(       Note: MSEs registered under MSMED Act and Startups recognized by ) Tj T*
(       DPIIT are EXEMPT from EMD as per GFR 2017 Rule 170\(i\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 3: EVALUATION METHODOLOGY) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.1  Evaluation shall be done in Two-Bid System:) Tj T*
(     \(a\) Technical Bid: Evaluated first. Only technically qualified bidders ) Tj T*
(         will have their Financial Bids opened.) Tj T*
(     \(b\) Financial Bid: L1 \(Lowest Bidder\) methodology.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.2  Technical Evaluation will be on Pass/Fail basis against the eligibility ) Tj T*
(     criteria listed in Section 2.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.3  The Evaluation Committee reserves the right to seek clarification from ) Tj T*
(     any bidder regarding their submission.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.4  Bidders scoring below the technical threshold will NOT have their ) Tj T*
(     financial bids opened.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 4: BID SUBMISSION REQUIREMENTS) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.1  Technical Bid Envelope shall contain:) Tj T*
(     \(a\) Covering letter on company letterhead) Tj T*
(     \(b\) EMD proof \(BG/FDR/DD\) or MSE/Startup exemption certificate) Tj T*
(     \(c\) Audited balance sheets for last 3 financial years) Tj T*
(     \(d\) CA certificate for average annual turnover) Tj T*
(     \(e\) Work completion certificates for similar works) Tj T*
(     \(f\) CPWD/MES/PWD registration certificate) Tj T*
(     \(g\) ISO 9001:2015 certificate) Tj T*
(     \(h\) Contract Labour License) Tj T*
(     \(i\) GST Registration Certificate) Tj T*
(     \(j\) PAN Card copy) Tj T*
(     \(k\) Self-declaration regarding non-blacklisting) Tj T*
(     \(l\) Company incorporation certificate) Tj T*
(     \(m\) Board resolution / Power of Attorney) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.2  Financial Bid: To be submitted ONLY in the prescribed BOQ format ) Tj T*
(     \(attached separately as BOQ_Price_Schedule.csv\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 5: GENERAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.1  The Competent Authority reserves the right to reject any or all bids ) Tj T*
(     without assigning any reason thereof.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.2  Conditional bids shall be summarily rejected.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.3  Joint ventures / consortia are NOT permitted for this tender.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.4  Sub-contracting of more than 25% of the work value is not permitted ) Tj T*
(     without prior written approval of the Competent Authority.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.5  All disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of courts in New Delhi.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
