(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ADDITIONAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS \(ATC\)) Tj T*
(Tender Ref: CRPF/EW/2025-26/BOP-RAJ/0042) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(NOTE: These Additional Terms and Conditions are SUPPLEMENTARY to the ) Tj T*
(General Terms and Conditions \(GTC\) of GeM and the terms in the RFP.) Tj T*
(WHERE THESE ATCs CONFLICT WITH THE STANDARD GTC, THESE ATCs SHALL PREVAIL.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-1: GEOGRAPHICAL EXPERIENCE REQUIREMENT \(ADDITIONAL\)) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(In addition to the experience criteria stated in the RFP \(Section 2.2\),) Tj T*
(the bidder MUST demonstrate experience of executing at least ONE civil ) Tj T*
(construction project in a desert/arid region \(Rajasthan, Gujarat-Kutch,) Tj T*
(or equivalent terrain\) within the last 5 years.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This is an ADDITIONAL mandatory requirement not covered in the standard GTC.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-2: SITE VISIT MANDATORY) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(Bidders are required to have visited at least ONE of the proposed BOP sites) Tj T*
(before bid submission. A Site Visit Certificate signed by the CRPF Station) Tj T*
(Commander at the respective location must be submitted with the Technical Bid.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Site visit window: 20th April 2025 to 5th May 2025.) Tj T*
(Contact for site visit arrangement: SE \(Border Works\), CRPF Jodhpur Sector.) Tj T*
(Phone: 0291-XXXXXXX) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-3: SECURITY CLEARANCE) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(The successful bidder's key personnel \(Project Manager, Site Engineer\) will) Tj T*
(be subject to security verification by CRPF Intelligence Wing before being) Tj T*
(permitted access to the border area construction sites.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Personnel who fail security clearance must be replaced within 15 days,) Tj T*
(failing which a penalty of Rs. 50,000 per day of delay shall be levied.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-4: MATERIAL PROCUREMENT) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(\(a\) All cement used shall be OPC 53 Grade conforming to IS 12269:2013.) Tj T*
(    Only cement from approved manufacturers \(ACC, Ambuja, UltraTech, ) Tj T*
(    Shree Cement, JK Cement\) shall be used.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(\(b\) Steel reinforcement shall conform to IS 1786:2008, Fe-500D grade.) Tj T*
(    Mill test certificates must be submitted for every lot.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(\(c\) Water for construction must be sourced locally. If potable water is) Tj T*
(    not available, the contractor must arrange water tankers at own cost.) Tj T*
(    Water testing report from a NABL-accredited lab required before use.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-5: MILESTONE PAYMENT SCHEDULE) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(Payment shall be released in the following milestones:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Milestone 1: Foundation complete \(30% of contract value\)) Tj T*
(  Milestone 2: Superstructure complete \(25% of contract value\)) Tj T*
(  Milestone 3: Finishing and MEP works \(25% of contract value\)) Tj T*
(  Milestone 4: Final completion + defect rectification \(15% of contract value\)) Tj T*
(  Retention: 5% retained for 24 months as defect liability period) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Note: GST shall be paid extra at applicable rates on each milestone payment.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-6: LIQUIDATED DAMAGES) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(In case of delay beyond the stipulated completion period of 12 months:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Penalty: 0.5% of contract value per week of delay) Tj T*
(  - Maximum penalty: 10% of total contract value) Tj T*
(  - Beyond 10% penalty: CRPF reserves the right to terminate the contract) Tj T*
(    and forfeit the Performance Security) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(ATC-7: REVISED TURNOVER REQUIREMENT) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(IMPORTANT AMENDMENT: The minimum average annual turnover requirement specified) Tj T*
(in the RFP \(Section 2.1.1\) is hereby REVISED from Rs. 5 Crore to Rs. 4 Crore ) Tj T*
(\(Rupees Four Crore Only\) to enable wider participation from competent firms.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This revision supersedes the original RFP clause. All other financial criteria) Tj T*
(remain unchanged.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
