(The following amendments are hereby made to the original NIT/RFP document) Tj T*
(dated 15th April 2025 and all associated documents:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(AMENDMENT 1: EXTENSION OF BID SUBMISSION DEADLINE) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(The last date for submission of bids is hereby EXTENDED as follows:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Original Date: 20th May 2025, 1400 hrs IST) Tj T*
(  Revised Date:  30th May 2025, 1400 hrs IST) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Original Date of Opening: 21st May 2025) Tj T*
(  Revised Date of Opening:  31st May 2025, 1100 hrs IST) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(AMENDMENT 2: EXPERIENCE CRITERIA CLARIFICATION) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(Clause 2.2.1 of the RFP is clarified as follows:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
("Similar Work" shall mean construction of residential/office/institutional) Tj T*
(buildings for Central Government, State Government, Defence establishments,) Tj T*
(or Central/State PSUs. Construction of commercial buildings, private ) Tj T*
(residences, or industrial sheds shall NOT be considered as "similar work.") Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Work completion certificates must clearly mention:) Tj T*
(  \(a\) Nature of work executed) Tj T*
(  \(b\) Gross value of the contract) Tj T*
(  \(c\) Date of completion) Tj T*
(  \(d\) Name and designation of the issuing officer) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(AMENDMENT 3: EMD FORMAT) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(In addition to BG/FDR/DD, the EMD may also be submitted as:) Tj T*
(  - Online transfer \(NEFT/RTGS\) to CRPF account) Tj T*
(  - Bid Security Declaration \(as per DoE OM dated 12.11.2020\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(MSE and DPIIT-recognized Startup exemptions continue to apply as per) Tj T*
(GFR 2017 Rule 170\(i\) and Rule 173\(i\) respectively.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(AMENDMENT 4: SOLAR POWER SPECIFICATION UPGRADE) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
(The solar power system requirement in Clause 1.2\(c\) of the RFP is revised:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Original: 5 KW per BOP) Tj T*
(  Revised:  7.5 KW per BOP \(to accommodate increased power requirements) Tj T*
(            for surveillance equipment\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The BOQ shall be deemed amended accordingly. Bidders should price for ) Tj T*
(7.5 KW solar systems in their financial bids.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(All other terms and conditions of the original NIT/RFP and ATC remain ) Tj T*
(unchanged unless specifically amended herein.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This Corrigendum is to be read in conjunction with the original tender ) Tj T*
(documents. In case of conflict between this Corrigendum and the original ) Tj T*
(documents, this Corrigendum shall prevail.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
